## Why Rails 8?

### Deployment Simplification
- **No PaaS required** - Deploy to any Linux server with Kamal 2
- **Reduced dependencies** - No Redis needed for most applications
- **Cost savings** - Use SQLite + Solid adapters instead of managed services

### Performance
- **Solid Cache** - Large, persistent caches using fast SSDs
- **Solid Queue** - Efficient job processing without Redis overhead
- **Propshaft** - Faster asset serving than Sprockets

### Developer Experience
- **Authentication generator** - No more Devise complexity
- **Integrated stack** - Everything works together out of the box
- **Modern defaults** - Hotwire, Importmap, TailwindCSS ready

### Production Ready
- **Proven in production** - Powers HEY, Basecamp (millions of users)
- **SQLite at scale** - Handles 100K+ requests/day per server
- **Solid adapters** - Battle-tested in real applications

